{{Use mdy dates|date=January 2016}}
{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of box office records set by ''Star Wars: The Force Awakens''}}
''[[Star Wars: The Force Awakens]]'' is the seventh film in the ''[[Star Wars]]'' franchise, released ten years after [[Star Wars: Episode III – Revenge of the Sith|the previous entry]]. Co-written and directed by [[J. J. Abrams]], the film stars [[Adam Driver]], [[Daisy Ridley]], [[John Boyega]] and [[Oscar Isaac]] in new roles, with [[Harrison Ford]], [[Mark Hamill]], and [[Carrie Fisher]] reprising their roles from the original trilogy [[Return of the Jedi|which concluded in 1983]]. Prior to its release, the film was predicted by box office analysts to break records, citing the relative lack of competition owing to its date of release, being released in large formats such as [[IMAX]] in a high number of venues, and multi-generational appeal to both fans of the previous movies and children as success factors.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/could-star-wars-open-at-789889|title=Could 'Star Wars' Open at $500 Million? The Force Is Strong|work=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=2018-08-05|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2015/08/star-wars-the-force-awakens-box-office-global-record-predictions-1201505170/|title=How 'Star Wars' Will Blow Up The Record Books With A $615M+ Global Opening|last=Tartaglione|first=Anthony D'Alessandro,Nancy|date=2015-08-26|work=Deadline|access-date=2018-08-05|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/aug/27/star-wars-the-force-awakens-predicted-world-record-opening-weekend|title=Star Wars: The Force Awakens set for record $615m opening|last=Child|first=Ben|date=2015-08-27|website=the Guardian|language=en|access-date=2018-08-05}}</ref>

''The Force Awakens'' was released in December 2015 and went on to break multiple [[box office]] records in various markets. The film set the worldwide records for the [[List of highest-grossing openings for films#Biggest worldwide openings on record|highest-grossing opening weekend]] and the [[List of fastest-grossing films#Fastest-grossing films to $1 billion|fastest to gross $1&nbsp;billion]].<ref name="SW2">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/12/star-wars-one-billion-dollars-global-box-office-record-second-weekend-overseas-results-1201673404/|title='Star Wars' Crosses $1B Global Box Office In Light Speed To Break 'World' Record; Offshore Cume At $546M – Update|last=Tartaglione|first=Nancy|date=December 27, 2015|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=August 4, 2018}}</ref><ref name="W">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/worldwideopenings.htm|title=Worldwide Openings|last=|first=|date=|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|accessdate=July 27, 2018}}</ref> In its domestic market of the United States and Canada, it set the records for the [[highest-grossing film]],<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/domestic.htm|title=All Time Domestic Box Office Results|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|language=en|access-date=2018-07-26}}</ref> opening day,<ref name="bodg">{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/days/?page=open&p=.htm|title=Top Opening Day Grosses|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=August 4, 2018}}</ref> [[List of highest-grossing openings for films#Biggest opening weekends in the U.S. and Canada|first]] through third weekends,<ref name="Opening_Weekends">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/|title=Opening Weekends|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=August 4, 2018}}</ref><ref name="2ndweekends">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/moreweekends.htm?page=2&p=.htm|title=Top Weekends: 2nd – 12th|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=August 4, 2018}}</ref><ref name="3rdweekends">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/moreweekends.htm?page=3&p=.htm|title=Top Weekends: 2nd – 12th|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=August 4, 2018}}</ref> and single calendar month,<ref name="SingleMonthGross">
* {{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/monthly/?view=calendargross&chart=bymonth&month=1&sort=titlegross&order=DESC&p=.htm|title=Box Office Results by Month - Box Office Mojo|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|language=en|access-date=2018-05-05}}
* {{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/monthly/?view=calendargross&chart=bymonth&month=2&sort=titlegross&order=DESC&p=.htm|title=Box Office Results by Month - Box Office Mojo|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|language=en|access-date=2018-05-05}}
* {{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/monthly/?view=calendargross&chart=bymonth&month=3&sort=titlegross&order=DESC&p=.htm|title=Box Office Results by Month - Box Office Mojo|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|language=en|access-date=2018-05-05}}
* {{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/monthly/?view=calendargross&chart=bymonth&month=4&sort=titlegross&order=DESC&p=.htm|title=Box Office Results by Month - Box Office Mojo|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|language=en|access-date=2018-05-05}}
* {{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/monthly/?view=calendargross&chart=bymonth&month=5&sort=titlegross&order=DESC&p=.htm|title=Box Office Results by Month - Box Office Mojo|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|language=en|access-date=2018-05-05}}
* {{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/monthly/?view=calendargross&chart=bymonth&month=6&sort=titlegross&order=DESC&p=.htm|title=Box Office Results by Month - Box Office Mojo|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|language=en|access-date=2018-05-05}}
* {{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/monthly/?view=calendargross&chart=bymonth&month=7&sort=titlegross&order=DESC&p=.htm|title=Box Office Results by Month - Box Office Mojo|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|language=en|access-date=2018-05-05}}
* {{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/monthly/?view=calendargross&chart=bymonth&month=8&sort=titlegross&order=DESC&p=.htm|title=Box Office Results by Month - Box Office Mojo|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|language=en|access-date=2018-05-05}}
* {{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/monthly/?view=calendargross&chart=bymonth&month=9&sort=titlegross&order=DESC&p=.htm|title=Box Office Results by Month - Box Office Mojo|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|language=en|access-date=2018-05-05}}
* {{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/monthly/?view=calendargross&chart=bymonth&month=10&sort=titlegross&order=DESC&p=.htm|title=Box Office Results by Month - Box Office Mojo|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|language=en|access-date=2018-05-05}}
* {{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/monthly/?view=calendargross&chart=bymonth&month=11&sort=titlegross&order=DESC&p=.htm|title=Box Office Results by Month - Box Office Mojo|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|language=en|access-date=2018-05-05}}
* {{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/monthly/?view=calendargross&chart=bymonth&month=12&sort=titlegross&order=DESC&p=.htm|title=Box Office Results by Month - Box Office Mojo|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|language=en|access-date=2018-05-05}}</ref> as well as the [[List of fastest-grossing films#Fastest-grossing films – US and Canada|fastest cumulative grosses]] through $900&nbsp;million.<ref name="fastestNumbers">{{cite web|url=https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/domestic/all-movies/fastest/fastest-to-900m|title=Fastest Movies to Earn $900 Million at the Domestic Box Office|website=[[The Numbers (website)|The Numbers]]|accessdate=August 4, 2018}}</ref> In other markets, it became the [[List of highest-grossing films in the United Kingdom|highest-grossing film in the United Kingdom]] and set opening weekend records in several countries including the UK, Germany, Australia, and Russia.<ref name="BFI2016">{{Cite book|url=https://www.bfi.org.uk/sites/bfi.org.uk/files/downloads/bfi-statistical-yearbook-box-office-2016-2017-06.pdf|title=The Box Office 2016|last=|first=|publisher=BFI Research and Statistics|year=2017|isbn=|location=|pages=3, 7|accessdate=August 4, 2018}}</ref><ref name="TG">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2015/dec/22/star-wars-the-force-awakens-uk-box-office-spectre|title=Star Wars: The Force Awakens gives UK box office a spectacular shot in the arm|last=Gant|first=Charles|date=December 22, 2015|website=[[The Guardian]]|accessdate=August 4, 2018}}</ref><ref name="UK4">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4134|title='Star Wars: The Force Awakens' Crushes Records, Topping Largest Box Office Weekend of All Time|last=Brevet|first=Brad|date=December 21, 2015|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=August 5, 2018}}</ref><ref name="ROW" />

A large proportion of the records were set in the domestic market of the United States and Canada. A comparative lack of ''Star Wars'' nostalgia and unfavourable currency exchange rates were identified as factors limiting the film's box office performance in other markets, while repeat viewings during the December holiday season boosted sales in the domestic market.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2016/01/star-wars-the-force-awakens-international-box-office-record-avatar-1201676082/|title='Star Wars: The Force Awakens' Vs 'Avatar': It's A Different Picture Overseas|last=Tartaglione|first=Nancy|date=2016-01-05|work=Deadline|access-date=2018-08-05|language=en-US}}</ref> A compounding factor is that whereas the US and Canada box office is closely tracked by sites such as [[Box Office Mojo]] and [[The Numbers (website)|The Numbers]], the same is not true for other [[Box office territory|box office territories]]. Many of the records set by the film are listed below. Data on the previous record and records that have since been surpassed are presented where available and applicable. All grosses are given in unadjusted [[United States dollar|US dollars]], except where noted otherwise.

