== Other territories ==
[[File:BFI London IMAX at night.jpg|thumb|250px|The [[BFI IMAX]] in [[London]] is the highest-grossing IMAX cinema in the world for ''The Force Awakens''.<ref name="Day13">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/12/star-wars-uk-record-imax-titanic-box-office-1201674347/|title='Star Wars' Overtakes 'Titanic' In UK; Sets Speed & IMAX Records|last=Tartaglione|first=Nancy|date=December 31, 2015|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|accessdate=August 4, 2018}}</ref>|alt=An aerial photograph of the BFI IMAX theatre in London at night]]Outside of the United States and Canada market, the film set opening records in one form or another in 30 different markets. The United Kingdom and Ireland market saw several records surpassed, including the record for the highest-grossing film of all time. Data on precise figures, previous record holders, and surpassed records is limited due to the absence of box office record trackers for these markets.
