==Extreme points within the UK==
In addition to the extreme points of the UK as a whole, the extreme points of [[England]], [[Northern Ireland]], [[Scotland]], [[Wales]] and for the island of [[Great Britain]] are listed below.

===Great Britain===
*Northernmost point &ndash; [[Dunnet Head]] at {{coord|58|40|N|3|22|W|region:GB-HLD_type:landmark}}, known also as Easter Head, [[Caithness]], [[Highland (council area)|Highland]]
*Southernmost settlement &ndash; [[Lizard (village)|Lizard]], Cornwall, England at {{coord|49|57|N|5|12|W|region:GB-CON_type:city}}
*Westernmost point &ndash; [[Corrachadh Mòr]], Highland at {{coord|56|42|N|6|13|W|region:GB-HLD_type:landmark}}
*Westernmost settlement &ndash; [[Grigadale]], Highland at {{coord|56|43|N|6|11|W|region:GB-HLD_type:city}}
*Easternmost point &ndash; Lowestoft Ness, [[Suffolk]] at {{coord|52|29|N|1|46|E|region:GB-SFK_type:landmark}}
*Easternmost settlement &ndash; [[Lowestoft]], Suffolk at {{coord|52|28|N|1|45|E|region:GB-SFK_type:city}}

===England===

====Including [[List of islands of England|islands]]====
*Northernmost point &ndash; [[Marshall Meadows Bay]], [[Northumberland]] at {{coord|55|48|N|2|02|W|region:GB-NBL_type:landmark}}
*Northernmost settlement &ndash; [[Marshall Meadows Bay|Marshall Meadows]], Northumberland at {{coord|55|48|N|2|02|W|region:GB-NBL_type:city}}
*Southernmost point &ndash; [[Pednathise Head]], [[Western Rocks, Isles of Scilly]] at {{coord|49|51|N|6|24|W|region:GB-IOS_type:landmark}}
*Southernmost settlement &ndash; St Agnes, [[Isles of Scilly]] at {{coord|49|53|N|6|20|W|region:GB-IOS_type:city}}
*Westernmost point &ndash; [[Crim Rocks]], Isles of Scilly at {{coord|49|53|N|6|27|W|region:GB-IOS_type:landmark}}
*Westernmost settlement &ndash; [[Bryher, Isles of Scilly|Bryher]], Isles of Scilly at {{coord|49|57|N|6|22|W|region:GB-IOS_type:city}}
*Easternmost point &ndash; [[Ness Point|Lowestoft Ness]], Suffolk at {{coord|52|29|N|1|46|E|region:GB-SFK_type:landmark}}
*Easternmost settlement &ndash; [[Lowestoft]], Suffolk at {{coord|52|28|N|1|45|E|region:GB-SFK_type:city}}

====English mainland====
*Northernmost point &ndash; Marshall Meadows Bay, Northumberland at {{coord|55|48|N|2|02|W|region:GB-NBL_type:landmark}}
*Northernmost settlement &ndash; Marshall Meadows, Northumberland at {{coord|55|48|N|2|02|W|region:GB-NBL_type:city}}
*Southernmost point &ndash; Lizard Point, Cornwall at {{coord|49|57|N|5|12|W|region:GB-CON_type:landmark}}
*Southernmost settlement &ndash; Lizard, Cornwall at {{coord|49|57|N|5|12|W|region:GB-CON_type:city}}
*Westernmost point &ndash; [[William Combe|Dr Syntax's Head]], [[Land's End]], [[Cornwall]] at {{coord|50|04|N|5|43|W|region:GB-CON_type:landmark}}
*Westernmost settlement &ndash; [[Sennen Cove]], [[Cornwall]] at {{coord|50|04|N|5|42|W|region:GB-CON_type:city}}
*Easternmost point &ndash; Lowestoft Ness, [[Suffolk]] at {{coord|52|28.87|N|1|45.77|E|region:GB-SFK_type:landmark}}
*Easternmost settlement &ndash; Lowestoft, Suffolk at {{coord|52|28|N|1|45|E|region:GB-SFK_type:city}}

The distance between the southernmost point (Lizard Point) and the westernmost point (Land's End) is only 38.5 kilometers.

