====Scottish mainland====
*Northernmost point &ndash; [[Dunnet Head]] at {{coord|58|40|N|3|22|W|region:GB-HLD_type:landmark}}, known also as '''Easter Head''', [[Caithness]], [[Highland (council area)|Highland]], [[Scotland]]
*Northernmost settlement &ndash; [[Skarfskerry]], [[Caithness]], [[Highland (council area)|Highland]], [[Scotland]] at {{coord|58|39|N|3|15|W|region:GB-HLD_type:city}}
*Southernmost point &ndash; [[Mull of Galloway]], [[Wigtownshire]] at {{coord|54|38|N|4|52|W|region:GB_type:landmark}}
*Southernmost settlement &ndash; [[Cairngaan]], [[Wigtownshire]] at {{coord|54|38|N|4|54|W|region:GB_type:city}}
*Westernmost point &ndash; [[Corrachadh Mòr]], [[Highland (council area)|Highland]] at {{coord|56|42|N|6|13|W|region:GB-HLD_type:landmark}}
